name: JokeJester
0:
”Alexa, use Joke Jester”
”Alexa, ask Joke Jester for a joke”
”Alexa, tell Joke Jester to tell me a joke”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: joke jester
des:
Joke Jester is a snarky and lovable clown that will give you a random joke to help brighten your day! Laugh, smile, and enjoy the jokes with this jester!

This skill will work by default on all Amazon Alexa Devices and no additional hardware is required. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
